thread.title: Athena IT-Group 2014/2015 EBITDA up at DKK 12.6 million
thread.title_full: BRIEF-Athena IT-Group 2014/2015 EBITDA up at DKK 12.6 million | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: Athena IT-Group 2014/2015 EBITDA up at DKK 12.6 million
text:
Sept 28 Athena It-Group A/S :
* 2014/2015 revenue 64.0 million Danish crowns ($9.6 million) versus 52.1 million crowns year ago
* 2014/2015 EBITDA 12.6 million crowns versus 10.8 million crowns year ago
* Sees 2015/2016 revenue of 67-70 million crowns
* Sees 2015/2016 EBITDA 15-17 million crowns Source text: bit.ly/1P109x8
 ($1 = 6.6616 Danish crowns) (Gdynia Newsroom)
